    "body": "This is for the upcoming 32.x, because I presume users and devs are more likely using a later distro. This comes with tool bumps, such as:\r\n\r\n* GCC 14 -> 15 (https://packages.debian.org/trixie/g++ -> https://packages.ubuntu.com/resolute/g++)\r\n* Clang 19 -> 21\r\n* Cmake 3.31 -> 4.2\r\n* Valgrind 3.24 -> 3.26",
